      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是StudentDB，然后连到一个判断节点。这个判断节点也叫GradeSync吗？还是说判断和同步是两个不同的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "判断节点是GradeSync，但菱形表示判断。如果判断通过，就进入实际的同步处理，那个是矩形节点，也叫GradeSync——对，名字一样但形状不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：StudentDB连到菱形的GradeSync判断节点，Yes分支连到矩形的GradeSync处理节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "同步完成后要更新LMS门户，然后这个门户需要循环回去重新触发判断，因为可能要处理下一个学生。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：GradeSync处理节点连到LMS门户，然后LMS门户回连到判断节点GradeSync。这样形成循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要处理判断不通过的情况，No分支也要有个出口。这个我们也用GradeSync命名，表示同步结束或记录日志。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
